---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy - FilePad">
    <section class="privacy-page">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="privacy-content">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>

                <h2>What FilePad Does</h2>
                <p>
                    FilePad is a macOS utility that adds Finder Services for video compression and a lightweight
                    FilePad strip for batch jobs. Compression runs locally on your Mac.
                </p>

                <h2>Your Data</h2>
                <p>
                    FilePad stores settings locally on your Mac. FilePad does not require an account and does not
                    operate a file-processing server.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When you compress a video, the file is processed locally and the output is saved next to the
                    original file.
                </p>

                <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>
                    FilePad may download FFmpeg binaries on demand and verifies checksums before use. This download
                    only happens when needed and does not include your files.
                </p>

                <h2>Analytics</h2>
                <p>
                    FilePad does not require analytics to function. If any optional usage metrics are introduced,
                    you will be able to disable them in Settings.
                </p>

                <h2>Updates</h2>
                <p>We may update this policy. Check back occasionally.</p>

                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:support@filepad.app">support@filepad.app</a></p>
                <p>See also: <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .privacy-page {
        padding: 120px 0 60px;
        min-height: 80vh;
    }

    .privacy-content {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .privacy-content h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1f2933;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        font-family: 'Space Grotesk', 'Work Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    }

    .last-updated {
        color: #6a6f7c;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .privacy-content h2 {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1f2933;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .privacy-content p {
        color: #6a6f7c;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .privacy-content a {
        color: #ff5d3b;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    .privacy-content a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }

    .privacy-content strong {
        color: #1f2933;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .privacy-page {
            padding: 100px 0 40px;
        }

        .privacy-content h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
